metadata.description:
Full length high-resolution: https://youtu.be/isYNW2M1-0Y 

Retro Spirals is the first NFT minted by Maths Town.  ID number 1.  This video features a retro themed Mandelbrot coloured using the Orbit Trap method. A spiral is used as the trap which creates some wild spiralling effects.

This NFT will be made available for download in 8k (7680x4320) and 4k (3840x2160).
metadata.name: Retro Spirals - A Mandelbrot Fractal Zoom
